=== 格鲁吉亚運動員意外事故 ===
於開幕當日，[[格魯吉亞|格魯吉亞]][[雪橇运动|雪橇]]运动员[[诺达尔·库马里塔什维利|诺达尔·库马里塔什维利]]於[[威士拿|威士拿]]備賽時被拋出，撞到鋼柱受伤，最终于当地时间周五不治身亡，終年二十一歲。<ref>{{cite news | coauthors =  | title = Olympic luger Nodar Kumaritashvili dies after crash | work = BBC | publisher =  | date = 2010-02-13 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/olympic_games/vancouver_2010/luge/8513595.stm | accessdate = 2010-03-03 | archive-date = 2010-03-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100311060428/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/olympic_games/vancouver_2010/luge/8513595.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref> 成為自1964及1992冬奧后第四位於奧運期間死亡的運動員。國際雪橇協會於意外後召開緊急會議，所有練習取消。

在開幕禮，格魯吉亞旗幟掛上黑布條，該國運動員亦帶上黑頸巾以示悼念。而大會當局亦在開幕禮之中為他默哀及下半旗。<ref>{{cite news | coauthors =  | title = Winter Olympics 2010: Nodar Kumaritashvili's death overshadows opening ceremony | work = [[衛報|衛報]] | publisher =  | date = 2010-02-13 | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/othersports/winter-olympics/7227952/Winter-Olympics-2010-Nodar-Kumaritashvilis-death-overshadows-opening-ceremony.html | accessdate = 2010-03-03 | archive-date = 2017-02-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170221011157/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/othersports/winter-olympics/7227952/Winter-Olympics-2010-Nodar-Kumaritashvilis-death-overshadows-opening-ceremony.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>

== 爭議 ==
=== 女子跳台滑雪 ===
IOC在2006年以女子跳台滑雪作為一個運動項目尚未發展齊全，並不符合許多作為奧運項目的基本條件為由，投票決定不包括女子跳台滑雪在2010年的冬季奧運項目內。這項決定引起了加拿大女子跳台滑雪國家隊的不滿，並因此向加拿大人權委員會投訴這決定的性別歧視元素，但最終投诉失败。<ref>{{cite news | coauthors =  | title = Groups to press IOC to allow women's ski jumping in 2010 Olympics | work = [[美國今日報|美國今日報]] | publisher =  | date = 2008-01-18 | url = http://www.usatoday.com/sports/olympics/2008-01-18-2335162792_x.htm | accessdate = 2010-03-03 | archive-date = 2011-06-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110604091343/http://www.usatoday.com/sports/olympics/2008-01-18-2335162792_x.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>

=== 日本速滑服疑似透视争议 ===
德国《柏林日报》报道高木美帆等日本速滑队员的着装为透视装，透过速滑服可以看到内衣。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.ifeng.com/sports/zonghe/201002/0212_4685_1545559.shtml |title=日本透视速滑服引争议 90后女队员内裤清晰可见 |accessdate=2010-02-13 |archive-date=2010-02-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100215144858/http://news.ifeng.com/sports/zonghe/201002/0212_4685_1545559.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>也有網民討論認為是設計顏色不當引起觀眾誤會，而那部份實際上為特別素材。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://vancouver2010.nikkansports.com/speedskating/news/p-sp-tp0-20100217-596891.html |title=スケート金スーツ股間の逆三角形が力の源 |accessdate=2019-04-14 |archive-date=2020-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200208171447/http://vancouver2010.nikkansports.com/speedskating/news/p-sp-tp0-20100217-596891.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 美國轉播商插播另類節目 ===
在閉幕式期間，美國[[全國廣播公司|國家廣播公司]]在聖火熄滅後插播"The Marriage Ref"清談節目。閉幕式的演唱會部份在其廣播網完成放送本地新聞後繼續播出。此舉令到很多人在[[Twitter|推特]]微博服務和其他社會交流網站表達不滿。
=== 禁藥醜聞 ===
2016年12月23日，IOC宣布將重驗俄羅斯運動員的樣本。而相關報告指出俄羅斯的禁藥醜聞起源於該屆冬季奧運會上的慘敗而開始，並且使其在[[2014年冬季奧林匹克運動會|下屆]][[2014年冬季奧林匹克運動會獎牌榜|在自家門口衝到第1名]]的位置。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.olympic.org/news/ioc-starts-disciplinary-procedures-against-28-russian-athletes-from-sochi-2014|title=IOC STARTS DISCIPLINARY PROCEDURES AGAINST 28 RUSSIAN ATHLETES FROM SOCHI 2014|date=2016-12-23|accessdate=2017-02-10|publisher=INTERNATIONAL OLYMPIC COMMITTEE|location=Lausanne, Switzerland|quote=The IOC will also re-analyse all samples from Russian athletes at the Olympic Winter Games Vancouver 2010.|archive-date=2020-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925075214/https://www.olympic.org/news/ioc-starts-disciplinary-procedures-against-28-russian-athletes-from-sochi-2014|dead-url=no}}</ref>

